cs.PL, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.AR 

The paper discusses a new functional language for describing optimization strategies for programs, which is relevant to programming languages (cs.PL) and machine learning (cs.LG) communities. The examples given in the paper are related to image processing (cs.CV) and deep learning (cs.AI), which further supports these categories. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of specialized hardware devices, which could also relate to the computer architecture (cs.AR) category.
